headline: Nvidia teams with Palantir to go after corporate logistics business
summary: WASHINGTON (Reuters) -Nvidia and Palantir Tech on Tuesday announced a deal in which Palantir will tap Nvidia's chips and software to help its customers speed up decision making in complex fields such as logistics.  Well-known as a defense contractor, Palantir's shares have risen this year, driven by increased defense spending on its military-grade AI tools.
